## ðŸ“Œ Course Structure

### **Module 1: Foundations of Modern Software Development**
- Development environment setup
- Version control basics
- Modern development practices
- Cloud computing fundamentals
- Full-stack development introduction

### **Module 2: Web Development Fundamentals**
- HTML5 & CSS3 basics
- JavaScript essentials
- React & Vue.js foundations
- Advanced framework concepts
- Web deployment & optimization

### **Module 3: Mobile Development**
- React Native basics
- Mobile UI development
- Data management
- Advanced mobile features
- App deployment

### **Module 4: Backend & API Development**
- Python and Django basics
- REST API design
- Authentication & security
- Database management
- Deployment & scaling

